{
  "stem": "13313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My little brother used to stand guard to see if anybody was coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would steal fruit, or in the fields, steal raw beets, and turnips, potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and whenever we were send to do the shopping for them, because we did the shopping, and the wood cutting, and take laundry to the laundry-- laundry-- not mats, but to the laundry places, which was always a few kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did all that work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whenever went to a bakery, or to a [? food ?] store, before we-- we used to swipe whatever we could, piece of bread, piece of candy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how we, more or less-- but, in the meantime, our health deteriorated badly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were pretty-- in good shape when we started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I would say within a couple of years we had-- we would look like-- like the pictures of the people that you see coming out of concentration camps, gaunt and-- and-- and like skeletons, and full of infections and warts, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the starvation part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, everything was raw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, everything-- no way of cooking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once in awhile, we got caught stealing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the people that we-- didn't realize who we were, so they would come and tell, complain to the Roggemans that we were caught in their garden stealing something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So naturally after-- this was always-- the-- the beatings, and after that were very, very fierce.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roggeman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roggeman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never mister, never.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
